data.description: Move in ready home located in Solana Ridge, with easy access to shopping and major highways all of what you need. Step inside and enjoy a nice living area which opens up into the dining room and kitchen area. Kitchen is updated with nice countertop space and large sink. Pantry and Utility room right off of kitchen with easy access. Upstairs has a nice loft with primary bedroom and bath next to 2 nice size secondary bedrooms. Nice covered Front porch with plenty of shade. Large backyard with plenty of room to grow.
